Format: Retail Epub and Retail PDF
Reader Required: 
PDF- Adobe Reader, Adobe Digital Editions
Epub- Adobe Digital Editions, Calibre, MoonReader for Android
Format conversion: convert epub to mobi (Kindle) with Calibre

NOTES: Barron's SAT Subject Test Chemistry 11E PAPERBACK version includes a CD-ROM with two tests, the ebook version DOES NOT include that but has four practice tests plus a diagnostic test. McGraw-Hill's SAT 2014 views better in Calibre, due to formatting on the workseets. They also have some practice tests on the website, with email registration required.

These are the only formats I could get my hands on, just use a reader as specified above. You can print out the worksheets with ADE, Calibre and Adobe Reader. Tested on the above readers with no problems.
Don't hesitate to PM me if you have any questions or problem with the download, as comments on the torrent are easy to miss. Please allow a couple seconds for the seedboxes to kick in, then it should move pretty quick.
Good luck! :D

Description from Barron's SAT Subject Test Chemistry, 11th Edition:
The updated edition of Barron's SAT Subject Test Chemistry includes: 
-A full-length diagnostic test with explained answers
-Four practice tests that reflect the actual SAT Subject Test Chemistry
-All questions answered and explained
-Detailed reviews covering all test topics
-Appendixes covering the Periodic Table, important equations, and more 

For 70 years, BARRON'S experts have been helping students surpass their expectations on standardized tests. This is the only book you will need to get the score you want on the SAT Subject Test in Chemistry. 
-Proven test-taking strategies that make the difference between a good score and a great score
-Four full-length model tests plus a diagnostic test in the book that reflect the actual test in length, question types, and degree of difficulty
-Additional features that include study tips, test-taking advice, a comprehensive subject review, information-packed appendixes, and extra practice questions with answers covering all test topics
-A test overview and an explanation of the test's scoring method
-Both teachers and test-taking students have praised earlier editions of this manual for its wealth of well-organized detail.
